Description
AuthorNotFoundException
Custom exception thrown when an author is not found in the system.
Book
Represents a book with details such as ID, title, author, category, and price.
BookClient
The BookClient class is a client application that interacts with the book management system.
BookImpl
BookImpl is an implementation of the IBook interface.
CategoryNotFoundException
Custom exception thrown when a category is not found in the system.
ElectionBooth
The ElectionBooth class provides the core functionality for checking the eligibility of a voter based on their age, locality, and voter ID.
IBook
IBook is an interface that defines methods for managing a collection of Book objects.
IdNotFoundException
Custom exception thrown when an ID is not found in the system.
LocalityNotFoundException
LocalityNotFoundException is thrown when a user's locality cannot be found in the system.
NotEligibleException
NotEligibleException is a custom exception used to indicate that a user is not eligible for a certain operation or process within the voter application.
NoVoterIDException
NoVoterIDException is a custom exception used to indicate that a user does not have a valid voter ID.
PriceNotAvailableException
Custom exception thrown when the price of an item (e.g., a book) is not available.
TitleNotFoundException
Custom exception thrown when a book title is not found in the system.
UnderAgeException
UnderAgeException is a custom exception used to indicate that a user is not eligible due to being under the required age limit.
Voter
The Voter class contains the main method to interact with the user and check their eligibility for voting based on their age, locality, and voter ID.
